00:52:06,000 --> 00:52:08,000
And so it can be really, really challenging.

341
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:10,000
And, you know, some players really love that, and that's awesome.

342
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:11,000
Definitely.

343
00:52:11,000 --> 00:52:12,000
Awesome.

