00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:32,000
And we've just opened that up to say damage, right?

363
00:53:32,000 --> 00:53:37,000
That's going to scale everything across your character as opposed to like while you're doing this sort of obscure thing.

364
00:53:38,000 --> 00:53:39,000
So we think that feels a lot better.

365
00:53:40,000 --> 00:53:45,000
We've also just sort of taken a look at what are the affixes we're giving, like fucking potion healing.

366
00:53:46,000 --> 00:53:48,000
Like I know you're all going to be really sad.

367
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:49,000
That was my favorite stuff.

