00:54:35,000 --> 00:54:42,000
And as you're journeying through Paragon, right, it should feel like you have more options than to just bum rush every glyph socket and every legendary node.

381
00:54:42,000 --> 00:54:49,000
There should be some pretty punchy, like, damage sources that you can get, damage reduction sources you can get.

382
00:54:49,000 --> 00:54:55,000
We've also done things like all the resistance nodes you have on the Paragon board actually give max resistance as well now.

383
00:54:56,000 --> 00:54:57,000
So it's pretty powerful.

384
00:54:57,000 --> 00:54:57,000
Yeah.

385
00:54:57,000 --> 00:54:58,000
We've done a lot of changes there.

386
00:54:59,000 --> 00:55:02,000
So this is one of the first steps we're taking to really improve the Paragon system.

387
00:55:03,000 --> 00:55:06,000
With the new sort of philosophy of, like, we want you to pick what boards you want.

388
00:55:07,000 --> 00:55:09,000
And we expect to be updating more in the future.

389
00:55:10,000 --> 00:55:10,000
Oh, yeah, absolutely.

