00:55:18,000 --> 00:55:25,000
And so we're basically just taking, like, the tons and tons of power that was in glyphs and kind of slightly redistributing it to Paragon.

392
00:55:25,000 --> 00:55:28,000
So going through your Paragon board is just more interesting and fun.

393
00:55:29,000 --> 00:55:29,000
Definitely.

