01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:43,000
And we saw this as an opportunity to essentially create an identity between the runecrafting of Mythic Uniques and the blacksmith.

524
01:02:43,000 --> 01:02:45,000
We moved it from the alchemist to the blacksmith.

525
01:02:45,000 --> 01:02:47,000
The blacksmith version of crafting Mythic Uniques.

526
01:02:48,000 --> 01:02:54,000
So now what you're going to be able to do is you're going to be able to take two Resplendent Sparks to the blacksmith and get a random Mythic Unique.

527
01:02:54,000 --> 01:02:58,000
That means no matter what, as long as you do everything in the season, you're going to get a Mythic Unique.

528
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:07,000
