529
01:03:07,000 --> 01:03:07,000
Right.

530
01:03:07,000 --> 01:03:10,000
And what that does is the runes are a lot more flexible.

531
01:03:10,000 --> 01:03:11,000
They can be traded.

532
01:03:11,000 --> 01:03:16,000
You can also get some incremental progress, right, because they drop a lot more frequently than Mythic Unique or Sparks in general.

533
01:03:17,000 --> 01:03:22,000
So what this means is you now have two really clear means to sort of target Mythic Uniques.

534
01:03:22,000 --> 01:03:27,000
And, you know, you now have a guaranteed way to make a Mythic Unique at the end of a season, which we think will feel really good.

535
01:03:27,000 --> 01:03:32,000
Something that's kind of cool about that is that it gives runes this, like, intrinsic trade value, which I kind of love.

536
01:03:32,000 --> 01:03:32,000
Yeah.

537
01:03:32,000 --> 01:03:38,000
Like, they have this big purpose towards crafting one of the best items in the game, which is really cool.

