01:07:51,000 --> 01:07:53,000
I also wanted to talk about Nature's Fury.

602
01:07:53,000 --> 01:08:03,000
This is a key passive that whenever you cast an Earth or Storm skill, there's a chance to cast the same skill of the opposite type.

603
01:08:04,000 --> 01:08:09,000
