01:09:05,000 --> 01:09:11,000
Especially whenever there's one build that's so dominant that it really makes it feel like, hey, I'm playing the class wrong if I'm not doing this.

617
01:09:11,000 --> 01:09:12,000
And that's not something that we want.

618
01:09:12,000 --> 01:09:21,000
